This paper deals with the problem of incentive design in multi-party machine learning systems, which involves game theory, optimization, and information theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
